    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; mean absolute error < 10%) across all 11 constructs and three independent modeling teams. Twelve of 13 V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged and the COU is explicitly scoped to ASTM F1717 standard test conditions. The ensemble modeling approach, inter-laboratory experimental validation, and quantitative UQ campaign collectively provide sufficient credibility evidence to support the Medium assurance level required for this Class II device application.",
